Class AppendingJsonTextJsonHandler

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonHandler<Void>

    public final class AppendingJsonTextJsonHandler
extends AbstractAppendingJsonTextJsonHandler<Appendable,Void>
    A AppendingJsonTextJsonHandler is a AbstractAppendingJsonTextJsonHandler that appends the handled JSON document as a pretty JSON text to a given Appendable and calculates no result.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Torsten Krause (tk at markenwerk dot net)
